            <title>[LU-11525] support for RHEL 7.6</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11525</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7.6 to be released, we need make Lustre support it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Release Notes for Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7.6 Beta:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://access.redhat.com/documentation/en-us/red_hat_enterprise_linux/7-beta/html-single/7.6_release_notes/index&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/documentation/en-us/red_hat_enterprise_linux/7-beta/html-single/7.6_release_notes/index&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;RC1 with kernel version 3.10.0-957.el7 is also available now.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
